The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Lara: Cricket needs T20
                                                   Lara: Cricket needs T20
                      
	Port of Spain: Brian Lara feels cricket is a dying sport, which has got a fresh lease of life in Twenty20  a format that has revived the spectators interest in the game.         
	Cricket is a dying sport and I believe that Twenty20 is going to be beneficial for many reasons, Lara said at a symposium here. This new form of game has brought a different spectator... Im very happy and very welcoming of the Twenty20 game. (PTI)                                                                                                                       
